  "detailHtml": "<p><img src=\"/assets/images/files/1432272958021509120_13cea773.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p><img src=\"/assets/images/files/1331924448667467776_90cbfc1f.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">平台所售谷歌账号不能用于充值消费，不可用于登录游戏，仅可用于游戏下载。（由于LOL登录修改了规则，谷歌新用户无法直接上游戏，必须绑定拳头号方可使用）</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap;\">【账号说明】：</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">空白新账号使用时请自行选择需要的国家并进行改区，（一年只可更改一次）</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap;\">【关于收货】：</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">您收到的换码内容顺序分别为：账号-密码-辅助验证邮箱 </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap;\">【特别说明】：</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">登录谷歌商店需要魔法工具；平台所售账号，只可用于商店下载使用，若用于其他用途或违返官方规则造成的后果请自行承担，谢谢~ </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px; font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap;\">【特别提醒】：</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">账号出售后包首登，非人为操作原因质保3天，收到账号后，请及时更改密码，有需要的可以绑定手机号；请妥善保管账号，并遵循平台规则使用</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">新手小白请先了解谷歌账号哦，可点击下方链接查看资料信息~ </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">谷歌新账号改国家：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/books/share/e90c5219-6ccd-46d8-a135-4b205825e05f/yh2nkf\" _src=\"https://www.yuque.com/books/share/e90c5219-6ccd-46d8-a135-4b205825e05f/yh2nkf\" target=\"_blank\">https://note.youdao.com/ynoteshare/index.html?id=5fffaff4ebb6a9b3aa51f14bdd3730ca&amp;type=note&amp;_time=1675157006798</a></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">谷歌账号登录教：</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Consolas, &quot;Lucida Console&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 20px;\">https://www.yuque.com/wyf7u4/cvpke5/oklq8g</span></p>",
